  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the myeolchi anchovies in cold water and drain well.",
    "In a large pan, heat the sesame oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the myeolchi anchovies and cook for 2 minutes until lightly browned.",
    "Add the ferment kimchi, soy sauce, salt, and black pepper, and stir-fry for 2 minutes.",
    "Divide the cooked brown rice into bowls.",
    "Top the rice with the anchovy and kimchi mixture.",
    "Garnish with chopped green onions and toasted sesame seeds.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
